---
title: Sweet 'n' Savoury Baked Chicken Breasts with Mashed Potatoes and Salad
description: This sweet-and-savoury glaze is inspired by the nostalgic "chili" sauce that you can grab from grocery store shelves. This homemade version is perfect on chicken and then some! Creamy mashed potatoes and a bright salad rounds out this plate perfect for anyone looking for a little walk down memory lane!
